 />\n之後訓覺，訓到十二點或者一點起身，可以開電腦睇劇，睇電影，打下機，有左電腦，呢個世界大把免費娛樂<br />\n<br />\n到左三四點，可能會覺肚餓，由於消耗唔多，可以考慮叫老散買份公司三文治俾我，或者餐蛋麵轉丁<br />\n<br />\nHEA到夜晚，如果有熟既散仔就叫佢同我一齊食，冇就自己睇住部65'電視食<br />\n<br />\n出咗獄咁耐，依照咁既生活方式，完全冇必要開支，總支出全撚部都係港豬納稅人俾<br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑，港豬辛苦工作，但六七十歲後，都冇得好似我咁住京士柏山，可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活<br />\n<br />\n原來殺咗人返香港已經可以做到，人生真係可笑，哈哈。"},{"pid":"789018f7b811a2d52852be5148392374e81d2e9a","tid":2515282,"uid":326804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518962d03fed07fff4c506b7b9371a03ba2db4d3","tid":2515282,"uid":152516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bd1cae79689e57c31a50096b78456ea3ecc857b","tid":2515282,"uid":369011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:41:31.000Z","msg":"條仆佳想幾時先自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:48:59.000Z","msg":"講真佢唔台灣 我地都吹唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"咪好似丁有康死都唔去大馬，奈佢唔何"},{"pid":"7310601c30cfdd36356caf733ddf83d69bf8005b","tid":2515282,"uid":25699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddf295833f643f44ea60eb3b1c1b86ae9033d0a","tid":2515282,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"4fa3c9161af8e6e5eabc57adc848d7bfd16fee73","tid":2515282,"uid":44171,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"eb710740a21dc29ede47b390cce8efce969eea7b","tid":2515282,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T01:37:43.000Z","msg":"因要港共要顯示台灣只係支共一個省，唔可以用國與國移交犯人規矩<br />\n本來只係一單殺人案，就變左政治大事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲死左唔少手足同坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src